Name: Financial Construction Financing

Caption.String: Specify the terms of up to five optional short-term construction loans. SAM calculates the total financing cost and adds it to the project's investment cost. The sum of percentages in the Percent of Installed Costs column must equal 100%.

const_per_percent1.Label: Construction Loan 1 percent of installed cost

const_per_percent2.Label: Construction Loan 2 percent of installed cost

const_per_percent3.Label: Construction Loan 3 percent of installed cost

const_per_percent4.Label: Construction Loan 4 percent of installed cost

const_per_percent5.Label: Construction Loan 5 percent of installed cost

const_per_percent_total.Label: Construction load total percent of installed cost

Equations: // construction interest calculation for each of the five construction period loans
f = ${const_per_percent1} / 100;       // percent of installed cost for loan principal
I = P * r / 12 * t / 2;                // loan interest
f = ${const_per_percent2} / 100;       // percent of installed cost for loan principal
I = P * r / 12 * t / 2;                // loan interest
f = ${const_per_percent3} / 100;       // percent of installed cost for loan principal
I = P * r / 12 * t / 2;                // loan interest
f = ${const_per_percent4} / 100;       // percent of installed cost for loan principal
I = P * r / 12 * t / 2;                // loan interest
f = ${const_per_percent5} / 100;       // percent of installed cost for loan principal
I = P * r / 12 * t / 2;                // loan interest
